issues.message: Use 'Akka.Actor.ICanTell' here; it is a more general type than 'Akka.Actor.IActorRef'.

Use 'System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable<System.Collections.Generic.KeyValuePair<Akka.Actor.Address, long>>' here; it is a more general type than 'System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary<Akka.Actor.Address, long>'.
Use 'System.Collections.Generic.ICollection<Akka.Actor.Address>' here; it is a more general type than 'System.Collections.Generic.IList<Akka.Actor.Address>'.
